{"tid":1847513,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"康文署明起停水陸設施","createTime":"2020-01-28T05:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T05:46:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"38d4fcbde4ace82f2744421cb9c8fd8d47b10db2","tid":1847513,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:44:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200128/PQFZ5YY47D32QLAF3X2234OW64/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200128%2FPQFZ5YY47D32QLAF3X2234OW64%2F&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=88253d78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200128%2FPQFZ5YY47D32QLAF3X2234OW64%2F&h=3f119eed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200128/PQFZ5YY47D32QLAF3X2234OW64/</a><br />\n<br />\n康文署明起停水陸設施<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200128/large/1580148136_7ef1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200128%2Flarge%2F1580148136_7ef1.jpg&h=4dc4774e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n康文署將由明日起，暫停開放多項設施，並取消在有關場地舉行的康樂、體育及文化活動，直至另行通告。<br />\n(社內相)<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】康樂及文化事務署今日宣佈，為配合政府「對公共衞生有重要性的新型傳染病預備及應變計劃」下提升應變級別至緊急及避免市民聚集，以下文康設施將由明日起暫停開放，並取消在有關場地舉行的康樂、體育及文化活動，直至另行通告。<br />\n<br />\n暫停開放的陸上和水上運動設施包括所有體育館、運動場、草地球場、人造草地足球場、網球場、壁球場、草地滾球場、高爾夫球設施、公眾游泳池、泳灘、屯門康樂體育中心、水上活動中心和度假營。文化設施則包括所有博物館、表演場地、公共圖書館及附設之自修室、流動圖書館，以及音樂事務處的音樂中心。"},{"pid":"30ae3af8199f75d92e7837d00ba709722fcc5d7a","tid":1847513,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5M3ShVs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5M3ShVs.png&h=9ebbd210&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b5dc35f372badba0e923696c43f3933e5148153","tid":1847513,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:45:10.000Z","msg":"一早應該啦"},{"pid":"01982d9fb98f538498f6a9590c7f681d1f6b1b7e","tid":1847513,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:46:45.000Z","msg":"坐咗幾耐?"}]}